name: Pacman Clone
tagline: Hot diggity damn its another pacman clone
body:
### Pacman!
This is just a small project that I created to learn about tilemaps. Feel free to download it and mess around with the test level. To be quite honest with you if you download this you must really have nothing better to do with your free time. I mean seriously read a book or something. Hell even taking a shit is probably a better use of your time.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with the website or the game? *Fuck off*.
